com.facebook.buck.jvm.java

Class JarFileObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.JarFileObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileObject, JavaFileObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaInMemoryFileObject, JavaNoOpFileObject

    public abstract class JarFileObject
extends Object
implements JavaFileObject
    A JavaFileObject implementation that allows using jar URIs unlike SimpleJavaFileObject that assumes the uri used is a file system uri. This implementation can be used when the CLASS_OUTPUT is represented by a straight to jar write. The only content that it stores is the full uri, the relative path within the jar and the kind of the FileObject.
